  title: Citizen Kane
  genre: Drama 2
  position: 42
  description: Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as
    a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning,
    tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears
    in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.
